{"tid":1390955,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"眾籌成立運輸界罷工基金有無得搞？","createTime":"2019-07-31T09:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:39:15.000Z","uid":282450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"89f493d144ff8c22726fbf47cf659f80a8d65ea3","tid":1390955,"uid":282450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%81%94%E8%87%B4%E5%A4%A7%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E5%89%8D%E9%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%2594%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25BF%2585%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%25A1%258C&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnd3lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=c74b6fe1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2581%2594%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25BF%2585%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%25A1%258C&h=6edbc266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%81%94%E8%87%B4%E5%A4%A7%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%84%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E5%89%8D%E9%A1%8C</a><br />\n<br />\n【文：陳德運】<br />\n老實說要全港三佰幾萬打工仔均參與全港大罷工的機會等於零。可是，要變相達致全港大罷工的方法卻是有可能的－<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港鐵及巴士前線車長罷工！</span>試問主要公共交通停止運作，跨區上班的打工仔仍可如常上班嗎？要令前線員工罷工不能只單靠「自發」參與，而是需要「罷工基金」作後盾。我們應發起眾籌罷工基金。基金保障對象限於港鐵及巴士前線員工。目的是要增加前線車長參與罷工的意欲。籌款金額到達某個款項，例如 2000 萬的話，就能減少前線車長參與罷工的經濟負擔，減少手停口停的問題，從而增加發生真正大罷工的可能。<br />\n<br />\n簡單而言，眾籌罷工基金有以下幾個重要效果：<br />\n<br />\n一、金錢保障前線員工罷工，增加前線參與罷工的意欲。<br />\n<br />\n二、確保罷工有持續性，不只是一兩天的象徵性罷工。<br />\n<br />\n三、了解民意的支持度。款項愈多，代表市民愈支持，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n四、不是把罷工流於口號宣傳，而是向政權確切發起的挑戰書。最理想的情況下，甚至罷工未啟動，權貴可能已經跪底，達到不戰而屈人之兵之效。 <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n香港雖然細，但大部分市民都好依賴公共交通<br />\n除咗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港鐵</span>、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">巴士</span>外，機場都好重要！<br />\n如果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">航空塔管制人員</span>以及航空公司的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">crew control</span>參與罷工<br />\n影響力可以好大！<br />\n所以，會唔會有巴/絲打熟識眾籌方式，成立運輸界嘅罷工基金！<br />\n<br />\n同意請推post<br />\n唔同意可直接ignore，推其他更有用嘅罷工post!<br />\n<br />\n#85齊罷工"},{"pid":"c06d7ea27fb98c19543e76917a6fe2672b0a46f0","tid":1390955,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:35:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VfuWZd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuWZd5.png&h=4576ca37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cSQ2oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cSQ2oL.png&h=cef8ee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkT1vED.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkT1vED.png&h=0accd33f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"6d93fb262bc7a3de1745810f4a6758cb679cccab","tid":1390955,"uid":110851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T09:35:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VfuWZd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVfuWZd5.png&h=4576ca37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cSQ2oL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cSQ2oL.png&h=cef8ee5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkT1vED.png\" data-thumbna